                        '***NO ONWARD CHAIN*** A BRAND NEW THREE DOUBLE BEDROOM, 2 BATHROOM DETACHED FAMILY HOME located in a SOUGHT AFTER RESIDENTIAL AREA within WALKING DISTANCE to POYNTON VILLAGE. HIGH SPECIFICATION FINISH throughout. DOWNSTAIRS WC. LOUNGE with FRENCH DOORS leading to the GARDEN, BESPOKE KITCHEN with QUARTZ WORKTOPS, SEPARATE UTILITY ROOM. MASTER BEDROOM with EN-SUITE SHOWER ROOM, two further bedrooms and STUNNING FAMILY BATHROOM with FOUR PIECE SUITE. DOUBLE WIDTH DRIVEWAY. ENCLOSED PAVED COURTYARD STYLE GARDEN.//n<b></b> //nConstructed in late 2021, this three bedroom detached family home has been built to exacting standards with a high specification finish throughout, which includes an air source heating pump system and underfloor heating. The property is located in a sought after residential area and ideally placed for both Poynton village and also Middlewood Way. //nIn brief the property comprises:- Entrance hall with open staircase leading to the first floor and storage cupboard below. Downstairs wc which is fully tiled with a modern two piece white suite and black fittings. The lounge has dual aspect windows allowing plenty of natural light and french doors lead directly onto the garden. The kitchen has been extensively fitted with a range of high quality shaker style wall base and drawer units which are further complemented by quartz worktops,  two ovens, ceramic hob, wine cooler and a dishwasher. A breakfast bar area offers the ideal space for informal dining and has further storage units below. A separate utility room provides ample laundry facilities. To the first floor the master bedroom benefits from an en-suite shower room which is fully tiled with a walk in double shower, low level wc and countertop wash basin, there are two further good sized bedrooms and a beautifully appointed family bathroom featuring a freestanding bath with wall mounted mixer tap, low level wc, separate shower cubicle with thermostatic hand and overhead mixer shower and countertop basin, the bathroom is fully tiled. Externally to the front of the property is a double width block paved driveway offering ample off road parking. The side garden has gated access and is fully enclosed by perimeter fencing and is low maintenance with modern contemporary paving.',
